sionate evaluation of an astonishing literary life.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 16. Mai 2019) 0aCartographerszScotlandvBiography. 0aHistorianszScotlandvBiography. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Literary.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2016z9783110485264oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUTP eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2015z978311066769108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Pilot 2014-2015z978311060681208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Pilot 2014-2019z978311065878108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press eBook Package 2014-2015z978311049093040uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/9781442619876423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781442619876.jpg  aPDA5EBK  a978-3-11-049093-0  University of Toronto Press eBook Package 2014-2015  a978-3-11-060681-2  University of Toronto Press Pilot 2014-2015  a978-3-11-065878-1  University of Toronto Press Pilot 2014-2019b2019  a978-3-11-066769-1  UTP eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA7ENG  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DKUb2016  aPDA14ALL  aPDA1ALL